    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable workhorse that's ready to hit the road? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for anyone who values function and reliability! While it shows some character through honest wear and tear and could use a little cosmetic TLC, it remains a solid performer that gets the job done. It\u2019s the perfect budget-friendly option for someone who needs a dependable driver without the premium price tag!",
