    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. The engine runs but has severe compression issues and multiple fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping. The body shows heavy rust in the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior has extensive wear and torn upholstery. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
